# Normalization

## DeSeq2 normalization and modeling
```{r}
dir.create(paste0(working.dir, "3-normalization"))
setwd(paste0(working.dir, "3-normalization"))

# set levels
se.filter$diet      <- factor(se.filter$diet,      levels=c("normal","high-fat"))
se.filter$sex <- factor(se.filter$sex, levels=c("male","female"))

# run deseq
dds <- DESeqDataSet(se.filter, design = ~ diet * sex)

dds <- DESeq(dds)
```

